NAME
    ips.pl - Patches a file with records provided from an IPS patch.

SYNOPSIS
        ips.pl myfilepatch.ips my.file

DESCRIPTION
    ips.pl is a revision of a Perl script found in the wild
    (<http://www.zophar.net/utilities/patchutil/ips-pl.html>) which will
    apply patches in the IPS format to the file specified. The IPS file
    format can be found at <http://zerosoft.zophar.net/ips.php>. It supports
    RLE (Run Length Encoded) IPS patches as well.

